@startuml
title YOLOv8 多策略优化框架（剪枝 + INT8量化 + 时空建模）

skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor Black
}

rectangle "原始YOLOv8模型\n约244MB" as BASE

rectangle "结构剪枝\n(Pruning)" as PRUNE
rectangle "INT8量化\n(Quantization)" as INT8
rectangle "时空上下文建模\n(Temporal-Spatial Modeling)" as TSM

rectangle "轻量化模型\n约89MB" as LIGHT
rectangle "嵌入式NPU加速推理\nRK3588等" as NPU

rectangle "检测结果\n(溺水/漂浮/挣扎)" as OUT

BASE --> PRUNE
PRUNE --> INT8
INT8 --> TSM

TSM --> LIGHT
LIGHT --> NPU
NPU --> OUT

note right of PRUNE
去除冗余卷积通道
降低参数量
end note

note right of INT8
FP32 → INT8
降低计算复杂度
提升NPU利用率
end note

note right of TSM
利用连续帧信息
增强行为识别能力
end note

@enduml